titlestmt.titleproper: Rockefeller Family Public Relations Department papers, Series 13
A Guide to the Rockefeller Family Public Relations Department papers, Series 13 FA1193

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on 2019-10-27 00:47:40 -0400.

did.unittitle: Rockefeller Family Public Relations Department papers, Series 13

physdesc.extent: 28 legal size record storage boxes 1 1/2 legal size record storage box 1 16x20 oversized record storage box

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The material remains in original order.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Type of records include: Reports, publications, newspaper articles, correspondence, reprints, architectural drawings and maps, and photographs

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Open for research with select materials restricted as noted. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC. Researchers interested in accessing digital media (floppy disks, CDs, DVDs, etc.) in this collection must use an access surrogate. The original items may not be accessed because of preservation concerns. To request an access surrogate be made, or if you are unsure if there is an access surrogate, please contact an archivist.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Information regarding the Rockefeller Archive Center's preferred elements and forms of citation can be found at http://www.rockarch.org/research/citations.php
